{"tid":1783199,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【軍事台】關於配備SM-3 IIA的神盾艦能否攔截洲際導彈的問題","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T14:28:06.000Z","uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f64ef7cdbfb0911c0f40f9a6496ecb79fea4bc00","tid":1783199,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"事原：響時事台同人嘈交，有人認為神盾系統不能攔截洲際導彈<br />\n立場：配備SM-3 IIA的神盾艦理論上有能力攔截洲際導彈<br />\n證據：<br />\n美國MDA官方文件重覆提及SM-3 IIA有能力響上升段同落下段攔截洲際導彈，只係冇能力響中段進行攔截，但不代表打唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://mostlymissiledefense.files.wordpress.com/2018/06/sm-3vsicbm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmostlymissiledefense.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F06%2Fsm-3vsicbm.png&h=99181401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mostlymissiledefense.files.wordpress.com/2016/06/blockiia-footprint5.png?w=768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmostlymissiledefense.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F06%2Fblockiia-footprint5.png%3Fw%3D768&h=cdf12d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國會批准FY2020進行SM-3 IIA攔截洲際導彈目標的計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.realcleardefense.com/articles/2019/09/06/lets_see_if_the_sm-3_block_iia_can_hit_an_icbm_114726.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realcleardefense.com%2Farticles%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2Flets_see_if_the_sm-3_block_iia_can_hit_an_icbm_114726.html&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWndxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=3dd2896c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.realcleardefense.com/articles/2019/09/06/lets_see_if_the_sm-3_block_iia_can_hit_an_icbm_114726.html</a><br />\n如果SM-3 IIA真係冇希望可以攔截洲際導彈，咁呢個測試根本就唔應該存在<br />\n另外：<br />\n<a href=\"https://insidedefense.com/daily-news/raytheon-confident-sm-3-block-iia-can-intercept-icbm-warheads\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finsidedefense.com%2Fdaily-news%2Fraytheon-confident-sm-3-block-iia-can-intercept-icbm-warheads&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWndxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=b4c8be93\" target=\"_blank\">https://insidedefense.com/daily-news/raytheon-confident-sm-3-block-iia-can-intercept-icbm-warheads</a><br />\n攔截彈製造商雷神有信心SM-3 IIA係可以攔到ICBM<br />\n<br />\n對方針對我話：燃盡速度唔等於攔截速度<br />\n解釋：要判斷一枚攔截彈能否攔截某種導彈，並唔係要睇攔截彈攔截時夠唔夠目標快，而係睇射程同射高夠唔夠、係睇intercept geometry<br />\n證據：2008年Operation Burnt Frost中，一枚未經升級的舊版SM-3 IA都能夠攔截速度遠遠超過佢速度、達到第一宇宙速度(超過7.8km/s)既低軌道衛星<br />\n<br />\n結論：關於SM-3 IIA能否攔截洲際導彈，理論上的確係可行，但由於未進行過實測，所以響美國MDA下次進行針對ICBM的攔截測試中就知分曉"},{"pid":"5dda8ef61bf9a30ecd64f69eeebc75c486d8ba07","tid":1783199,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44f89057b7ac7c3a92d22f474124bc9e5a7e5c73","tid":1783199,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"算啦 軍事撚話啱就啱啦 只要佢哋想嘅 美軍都可以變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}